  "body": "Hi there!\r\nWhile developing [Chainlink](https://github.com/smartcontractkit/chainlink), which uses go-ethereum's rpc.Client libraries, we were unable to gracefully shutdown our node. We've traced it back to our inability to [`Unsubscribe`](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/127553253e8d21cfbcd38edf3119ce81275c0454/rpc/client.go#L749) our websocket rpc.Client. We've reproduced the problem using exclusively `go-ethereum` code and appreciate any insight. We're also open to fixing the bug ourselves if pointed in the right direction.\r\n\r\nThanks in advance for any help.\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version:\r\nVersion: 1.8.16-stable\r\nArchitecture: amd64\r\nProtocol Versions: [63 62]\r\nNetwork Id: 1\r\nGo Version: go1.11\r\nOperating System: darwin\r\nGOPATH=/Users/dimroc/go\r\nGOROOT=/usr/local/Cellar/go/1.11/libexec\r\n\r\nOS & Version: OSX\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n[`*rpc.Client#Unsubscribe`](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/127553253e8d21cfbcd38edf3119ce81275c0454/rpc/client.go#L749) returns and does not block indefinitely.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n[`*rpc.Client#Unsubscribe`](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/127553253e8d21cfbcd38edf3119ce81275c0454/rpc/client.go#L749) blocks indefinitely.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\n[![asciicast](https://asciinema.org/a/204548.png)](https://asciinema.org/a/204548)\r\n\r\nFor a preconfigured reproduction, please see: https://github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe\r\n\r\n1. Run geth \r\n2. Run and attach a go-ethereum client\r\n3. subscribe to newHeads and logs\r\n4. Listen to a handful of heads and logs\r\n5. Kill all processes simultaneously\r\n6. Run `ps` and notice the client is blocked.\r\n7. Use [dlv](https://github.com/derekparker/delve) to investigate.\r\n\r\nAgain, this is set up and done for you in https://github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe.\r\n\r\nThis issue is spurious, but in practice it reproduces 75% of the time.\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n```\r\n(dlv) stack\r\n 0  0x000000000402fa3b in runtime.gopark\r\n    at /usr/local/Cellar/go/1.11/libexec/src/runtime/proc.go:303\r\n 1  0x000000000403ef1d in runtime.selectgo\r\n    at /usr/local/Cellar/go/1.11/libexec/src/runtime/select.go:313\r\n 2  0x000000000430dcc7 in github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe/vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*Client).send\r\n    at ./vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/client.go:460\r\n 3  0x000000000430c965 in github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe/vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*Client).CallContext\r\n    at ./vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/client.go:301\r\n 4  0x000000000430c5ff in github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe/vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*Client).Call\r\n    at ./vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/client.go:283\r\n 5  0x000000000431095d in github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe/vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*ClientSubscription).requestUnsubscribe\r\n    at ./vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/client.go:832\r\n 6  0x000000000431327d in github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe/vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*ClientSubscription).quitWithError.func1\r\n    at ./vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/client.go:761\r\n 7  0x0000000004070403 in sync.(*Once).Do\r\n    at /usr/local/Cellar/go/1.11/libexec/src/sync/once.go:44\r\n 8  0x000000000430ff55 in github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe/vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*ClientSubscription).quitWithError\r\n    at ./vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/client.go:755\r\n 9  0x000000000430fe98 in github.com/dimroc/geth-blocks-unsubscribe/vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc.(*ClientSubscription).Unsubscribe\r\n    at ./vendor/github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/rpc/client.go:750\r\n10  0x00000000043148a6 in main.main\r\n    at ./main.go:47\r\n11  0x000000000402f647 in runtime.main\r\n    at /usr/local/Cellar/go/1.11/libexec/src/runtime/proc.go:201\r\n12  0x000000000405b381 in runtime.goexit\r\n    at /usr/local/Cellar/go/1.11/libexec/src/runtime/asm_amd64.s:1333\r\n````\r\n",
